des: Gabriel Arias grounds into a double play, second baseman Tyler Fitzgerald to first baseman Logan Wyatt.   Zack Collins out at 2nd.    Gabriel Arias out at 1st.
Zack Collins singles on a line drive to right fielder Heliot Ramos.   Will Brennan to 2nd.
Will Brennan singles on a ground ball to left fielder Wade Meckler.
